pacman
Class State

java.lang.Object
  pacman.State

public class State
extends Object

A class representing a state of a Pac-Man board, as defined by the pacman.Game class. Contains the location of Pac-Man and the ghosts, as well as the remaining dots on the board. Equals and hashCode are defined on all fields EXCEPT the parent.
